@startuml
autonumber
actor "ATCC" as ATCC
participant ":System" as System

activate ATCC
ATCC -> System : registerAircraft(registrationNumber, modelName,\n manufacturingDate, seatingCapacity, currentStatus)
activate System

note right of System: The system validates the input,\nchecks if the model exists,\nand registers the new aircraft instance.

System --> ATCC : informs operation success and returns created aircraft
deactivate System
deactivate ATCC
@enduml